sentences.english: Yuxiang feels that the money is well spent.
sentences.chinese: 診費不便宜，玉香還是覺得很值得。

sentences.english: Doctors will not receive fares for services if patients are not able to pay.
sentences.chinese: 如果病人無力支付，醫生會免收診費。

sentences.english: This policy gives unlimited cover for hospital charges and specialist fees.
sentences.chinese: 這種保險單爲住院醫療費和專家門診費提供無限保險。
